### 测试健康检查（GET请求）
GET http://localhost:8080/ping

### 依赖健康检查（MySQL/Redis/VM）
GET http://localhost:8080/healthz/deps

### 注册机器（POST请求）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/machines/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "machine_id": "manual-test-node-001",
    "ip": "192.168.1.100",
    "hostname": "test-server",
    "status": "active"
}

### 幂等更新同一机器（重复注册不报错）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/machines/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "machine_id": "manual-test-node-001",
    "ip": "192.168.1.101",
    "hostname": "test-server-updated",
    "status": "active"
}

### 查看最近告警事件（MVP）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/alerts/recent?limit=20

### 按机器过滤最近告警
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/alerts/recent?machine_id=manual-test-node-001&limit=20

### 仅查看触发告警（P0）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/alerts/recent?level=P0&limit=20

### 仅查看恢复事件（RECOVERY）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/alerts/recent?level=RECOVERY&limit=20

### 仅查看通知失败的告警
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/alerts/recent?notify_status=failed&limit=20